
+------------------------------------------------------------------+
|  HTML::KTemplate v1.01 - Perl module to process HTML templates.  |
+------------------------------------------------------------------+


INSTALLATION
------------

To install, unzip and untar the archive, then type in the directory created:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


CHANGES
-------

1.01  Sat Sep 07 15:17:00 2002
	- template path can now be set with new()

1.00  Thu Sep 05 10:36:00 2002
	- first public release


